PURPOSE:
  Android 13+ "Material You" themed icons. When the user enables themed
  icons, Android extracts a colour from their wallpaper and tints this
  silhouette with that colour. Result: your icon harmonises with their
  home screen colour theme.

RULES FOR THIS LAYER:
  • Use ONLY #000000 as fill colour — Android replaces it at runtime
  • Pure silhouette — no grain lines, no highlights, no gradients
  • Same chair shape as the foreground, simplified to one solid form
  • All art within the 66dp safe zone

HOW TO ACTIVATE:
  Uncomment the <monochrome> line in:
    res/mipmap-anydpi-v26/ic_launcher.xml
    res/mipmap-anydpi-v26/ic_launcher_round.xml
-->

